{"tid":1729741,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"唯一幫到poly手足嘅方法","createTime":"2019-11-17T10:42:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T10:48:42.000Z","uid":130968,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"eab24b4b3e9ab0c72cf75950020bab8d5e192841","tid":1729741,"uid":130968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T10:42:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">就係燒狗屋</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n當初圍狗屋唔work係因為佢地係入面養尊處優 資源同數量都佔優 但而家佢總動員都圍攻poly嘅時候呢個前設就冇左 上次中大大埔開花都係冇狗理 係到有手足話要攻狗屋先有狗列陣同有狗車回防 <br />\n<br />\n所以要救poly就必需將全港狗屋/狗宿燒清光 搞到最大！<br />\n<br />\n利申：玩緊gta"},{"pid":"71f5050d2b1f118acb33faaa5569ee92a4de8d4e","tid":1729741,"uid":130968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T10:42:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ac835b8763e242f1ef719d44ba41973e07f0814b","tid":1729741,"uid":130968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T10:42:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"dd2d1b0e6b5970885c91e0100592924fcd9a5096","tid":1729741,"uid":130968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T10:42:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e53a26b3b76b68bbe47a51e5d60e863119255b9","tid":1729741,"uid":181035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T10:43:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eccdce7d0a08025bce0305763c6a19fbf8943b4b","tid":1729741,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T10:44:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"67544533b1160fa6040d4138ff4afaf0a7cfff2e","tid":1729741,"uid":338712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T10:48:42.000Z","msg":"以上次中大一戰作參考，晚上有好大機會發生激烈衝突，加上popo經上次一役之後，戰術必有改善，<br />\n<br />\n而且中大一戰，popo只派一水炮車，<br />\n對比今次(一水炮、二鋭武、音波炮），而且旺角與poly非常近，所以加上旺角警力，可説popo今次差唔多總動員到poly<br />\n<br />\n另外學校報警、示威者取危險物品、使用弓箭、巨型亞叉等，popo可以此藉口，全面進入校園拘捕或使用致命武力。這必令各手足有慘重傷亡。<br />\n<br />\n個人認為popo正等待夜晚，街上人流減少，然後開戰。<br />\n<br />\n各前線手足，如果popo有任何唔妥，請唔好留，唔好送頭，唔好受傷，我哋一個都不能少。<br />\n<br />\n其他人，可選擇各區花、到中環集會或到poly支援。"}]}